# Keep the build context small + clean — never ship host artifacts.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.tsbuildinfo
**/coverage
**/.turbo
apps/tauri-pos/src-tauri/target
apps/control-desktop/src-tauri/target
# Native mobile build output. The api and worker images contain no mobile
# code at all, yet these were being streamed into every build context:
# 2.7 GB of generated Android resources and 481 MB of iOS artifacts. That is
# what filled the build disk and failed a worker build mid deploy.
**/android/app/build
**/android/build
**/android/.gradle
**/ios/build
**/ios/Pods
**/ios/DerivedData
**/.expo
.git
.github
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/*.log
.claude
docs
*.md
deploy
